aS"18k Yellow Gold Filled Smooth Charming Women Earrings Wedding Hoop Jewelry HotClick to EnlargeClick to EnlargeClick to Enlarge\xc2\xa0Material18K Yellow Gold FilledSize13MM * 5MM \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 \xc2\xa0 (conversion: \xc2\xa01 inch = 25.4mm or 1mm = 0.0393 inch)Retail Price$18Package included1Pair Weight3g\xc2\xa0Kindly note:\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0The Real Item color which you receive maybe vary from the listing picture because of different Camera lens, and different light environment.\xc2\xa0Item Measure by hand, it could \xc2\xa0be \xc2\xa0a little different.What is gold filled ?\xc2\xa0Gold Filled Jewelry is a thick (about 25mil) solid layer of quality gold heat bonded onto an internal semi-precious metals by advanced mechanical process. It has all the great characteristics of solid gold jewelry without price tag . Please do not compare gold filled jewelry to plated jewelry (usually only 3 mil layer) as there is no comparison, gold filled is much more valuable and tarnish resistant than plated. It does not flake off, tarnish or discolor. It is extremely long lasting and if taken care of will last you a lifetime. Gold filled jewelry is an economical alternative to solid gold jewelry! Although it isn\xe2\x80\x99t solid gold jewelry.\xc2\xa0What causes gold to be different colors ?\xc2\xa0While pure gold is a warm yellow, it can be manufactured in a wide variety of colors-including pink, white, green, blue or gray-by being mixed with different metals. For example, when silver and copper are added to pure gold, it turns yellow. When nickel or palladium (or zinc and copper) are added, gold turns white. Pure gold combined with silver, copper and zinc results in green gold. And pink gold is made when copper is mixed with pure gold.\xc2\xa0What is the best way to care for the gold filled jewelry ?\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0Do not wear your jewelry in hot tubs and swimming pools. Take jewelry off when using laundry or cleaning products. NEVER, NEVER clean it with bleach.Use jewelry cleaner and a soft cloth to clean your gold filled jewelry .If you do not have jewelry cleaner, you can use mild soap and warm water. Never use any harsh cleaners such as bleach or abrasives. \xc2\xa0To store gold filled jewelry, wrap each piece separately in a soft cloth. Lay herringbone chains flat so they do not kink. Always remember to remove your jewelry before sleeping, bathing or exercising.Return Policy:\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0We accept returns within 30 days you are received the item, Buyer pay shipping fee.In case you received a wrong item, Items must be returned in its original and unused condition & must also be in its original box and packing.We do not allow refunds or exchanges because of change of mind. Apply pH Bond.Apply Gelish Foundation Gel in a THIN application and seal the edges of the nail.Place hand in the LED light for 10 seconds or 1 minute in UV Lamp.Apply Gelish Color in a thin application from cuticle to free edge.Place hand in the LED light for 30 seconds or 2 minutes in UV Lamp.Apply Gelish Top-It-Off Top Sealer.Place hand in the LED light for 30 seconds or 2 minutes in UV Lamp.Wipe off the tacky layer with Cleaser.Apply NOURISH Cuticle Oil to the skin surrounding the nail.For more information, visit http://www.gelish.com/Gelish Harmony Color Chart"

aS'How to play: \xc2\xa01<Use an ordinary dark coloured crayon or marker to draw a line on a white piece of paper. \xc2\xa02<Turn on switch on the button of the car. \xc2\xa03<Place car on top of the drawn line. \xc2\xa04<The car will run on the line automatically. \xc2\xa05<If the line finishes, the vehicle will continue in the direction followed from the previous line. \xc2\xa06<If the line is too thin, the vehicle may stray off the line, please make the line thicker (The line should be a quarter inch in thickness )Feature: \xc2\xa0This is a novelty inductive car, which follows the marker line like magic. \xc2\xa0If you place the Inductive car somewhere else it would run in circles until it finds the line. \xc2\xa0The Toy has an optical sensor that reads the black line drawn on a white piece of paper. \xc2\xa0The car is powered by 4 x AG 13 button cell.
